    <item>
      <title>用本地 AI 自动生成文章简介和标签：LM Studio 实践</title>
      <link>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0-ai-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BElm-studio-%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 21:25:37 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0-ai-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BElm-studio-%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;在编写文章的过程中，我常常会遇到怎么写简介可以让人一眼看出你想讲什么，以及给文章打上什么标签和分类，这些繁琐的工作常常消耗了我大量的精力（特别是文章多的时候），那么为了专注于文章内容本身，我们可以借助&lt;strong&gt;ai&lt;/strong&gt;来帮助我们在发布之前就进行补全，在开始先介绍一下我的电脑配置，有助于如何选择合适的&lt;strong&gt;大模型&lt;/strong&gt;，如下图&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;320&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;187&#34;&#xA;    srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-480.jpg 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-800.jpg 800w&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    data-native-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg%20320w,%20/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-480.jpg%20480w,%20/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-800.jpg%20800w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;eager&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;high&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;alt text&#34;&#xA;    data-image-state=&#34;ready&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;gallery-image&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-strategy=&#34;eager&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-avif=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-webp=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-fallback=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/ed491f7cd908/84dd2c5eb85e/responsive_content-fallback-800.jpg&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;410px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;170&#34;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;主要看显卡显存和内存大小，8G显存这一级别下，最优解应该是qwen3.6 35b a3b模型，专家架构可以显著提高输出速度，减少性能需求，选择了大模型后，接下来就是选择管理大模型的工具了，最主流的应该是&lt;strong&gt;LM studio&lt;/strong&gt;和&lt;strong&gt;ollama&lt;/strong&gt;，在这里我推荐LM studio，因为它有图形化界面，配置方便，下面是针对本机的参数调整界面&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-placeholder-48.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;320&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;191&#34;&#xA;    data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-480.jpg 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-800.jpg 800w&#34;&#xA;    data-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg%20320w,%20/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-480.jpg%20480w,%20/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-800.jpg%20800w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;alt text&#34;&#xA;    data-image-state=&#34;loading&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;gallery-image stack-lazy-image&#34;&#xA;    data-lazy-image=&#34;true&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-strategy=&#34;eager&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-avif=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-webp=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-fallback=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/3c333803de25/42e456383817/responsive_content-fallback-800.jpg&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/span&gt;实测处理单篇博文可以达到30token/s，接下来遇到的难题是怎么连到原有的部署流程，这涉及到程序之间端口的通讯，恰好LM studio有方便的本地端口1234，具体实现可以用ai写&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GitHub Pages 太慢怎么办：用 OSS 和 CDN 给博客提速</title>
      <link>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/github-pages-%E5%A4%AA%E6%85%A2%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%E7%94%A8-oss-%E5%92%8C-cdn-%E7%BB%99%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%8F%90%E9%80%9F/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 22:16:51 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/github-pages-%E5%A4%AA%E6%85%A2%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%E7%94%A8-oss-%E5%92%8C-cdn-%E7%BB%99%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%8F%90%E9%80%9F/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;之前因为源站是在国外Github平台上的原因，所以即使在国内接入了阿里云的esa，移动运营商的部分地区还是访问不上会报525，严重妨碍了我在同学面前装逼，于是今天我痛定思痛，决心改变这一现状，所以我开通了阿里云oss&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;320&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;174&#34;&#xA;    srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef