9ff/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-fallback=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/06ef141dfef2/e1fe0a9309ff/responsive_content-fallback-800.jpg&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;441px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;184&#34;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;为什么选择它呢，主要是因为它也可以做静态博客，虽然配置相比github pages较为复杂，并且还会收取一定费用（不多），但是对于国内的网络环境较为友好，在配置oss时一定要注意防盗链相关的选项，避免流量被盗刷而受到天价帐单，这是相关收费标准&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/c1f5e1c32849/4539761b31b8/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#x